The paper deals with machine learning techniques for training classifiers in multi-stage processes. The paper combines adversarial autoencoders, multi-task learning, and multi-label semi-supervised learning to address the challenges of underfitting and overfitting in such processes. The paper's focus on machine learning techniques and applications makes it likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
